quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  37,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  37,1,Wassaaaffaati saffaa
  37,2,Fazzaajiraati zajraa
  37,3,Fattaaliyaati Zikra
  37,4,Inna Illaahakum la Waahid
  37,5,Rabbus samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumaa wa Rabbul mashaariq
  37,6,Innaa zaiyannas samaaa 'ad dunyaa bizeenatinil kawaakib
  37,7,Wa hifzam min kulli Shaitaanim maarid
  37,8,Laa yassamma 'oona ilal mala il a'alaa wa yuqzafoona min kulli jaanib
  37,9,Duhooranw wa lahum 'azaabunw waasib
  37,10,Illaa man khatifal khatfata fa atba'ahoo shihaabun saaqib
  37,11,Fastaftihim ahum ashaddu khalqan am man khalaqnaa; innaa khalaqnaahum min teenil laazib
  37,12,Bal'ajibta wa yaskharoon
  37,13,Wa izaa zukkiroo laa yazkuroon
  37,14,Wa izaa ra aw Aayatinw yastaskhiroon
  37,15,Wa qaalooo in haazaa illaa sihrum mubeen
  37,16,'A-izaa mitnaa wa kunnaa turaabanw wa 'izaaman 'ainnaa lamab'oosoon
  37,17,Awa aabaa'unal awwaloon
  37,18,Qul na'am wa antum daakhiroon
  37,19,Fa innamaa hiya zajra tunw waahidatun fa izaa hum yanzuroon
  37,20,Qa qaaloo yaa wailanaa haazaa Yawmud-Deen�(section 1)
  37,21,Uhshurul lazeena zalamoo wa azwaajahum wa maa kaanoo ya'budoon
  37,22,Uhshurul lazeena zalamoo wa azwaajahum wa maa kaanoo ya'budoon
  37,23,Min doonil laahi fahdoohum ilaa siraatil Jaheem
  37,24,Wa qifoohum innahum mas'ooloon
  37,25,Maa lakum laa tanaasaroon
  37,26,Bal humul Yawma mustaslimoon
  37,27,Wa aqbala ba'duhum 'alaa ba'diny yatasaaa'aloon
  37,28,Qaalooo innakum kuntum taatoonanaa 'anil yameen
  37,29,Qaaloo bal lam takoonoo mu'mineen
  37,30,Wa maa kaana lanaa 'alaikum min sultaanim bal kuntum qawman taagheen
  37,31,Fahaqqa 'alainaa qawlu Rabbinaaa innaa lazaaa'iqoon
  37,32,Fa aghwainaakum innaa kunnaa ghaaween
  37,33,Fa innahum Yawma'izin fil'azaabi mushtarikoon
  37,34,Innaa kazaalika naf'alu bil mujrimeen
  37,35,Innahum kaanooo izaa qeela lahum laaa ilaaha illal laahu yastakbiroon
  37,36,Wa yaqooloona a'innaa lataarikooo aalihatinaa lishaa'irim majnoon
  37,37,bal jaaa'a bilhaqqi wa saddaqal mursaleen
  37,38,Innakum lazaaa'iqul 'azaabil aleem
  37,39,Wa maa tujzawna illaa maa kuntum ta'maloon
  37,40,Illaa 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
  37,41,Ulaaa'ika lahum rizqum ma'loom
  37,42,Fa waakihu wa hum mukramoon
  37,43,Fee jannaatin Na'eem
  37,44,'Alaa sururim mutaqaa bileen
  37,45,Yutaafu 'alaihim bikaasim mim ma'een
  37,46,Baidaaa'a laz zatil lish shaaribeen
  37,47,Laa feehaa ghawlunw wa laa hum 'anhaa yunzafoon
  37,48,Wa 'indahum qaasiraatut tarfi 'een
  37,49,Ka annahunna baidum maknoon
  37,50,Fa aqbala ba'duhum 'alaa badiny yatasaaa 'aloon
  37,51,Qaala qaaa'ilum minhum innee kaana lee qareen
  37,52,Yaqoolu a'innnaka laminal musaddiqeen
  37,53,'A-izaa mitnaa wa kunnaa turaabanw wa 'izaaman 'ainnaa lamadeenoon
  37,54,Qaala hal antum muttali'oon
  37,55,Fattala'a fara aahu fee sawaaa'il Jaheem
  37,56,Qaala tallaahi in kitta laturdeen
  37,57,Wa law laa ni'matu Rabbee lakuntu minal muhdareen
  37,58,Afamaa nahnu bimaiyiteen
  37,59,Illa mawtatanal oola wa maa nahnu bimu'azzabeen
  37,60,Inna haazaa falya'ma lil'aamiloon
  37,61,Limisli haaza falya'ma lil 'aamiloon
  37,62,Azaalika khairun nuzulan am shajaratuz Zaqqom
  37,63,Innaa ja'alnaahaa fitnatal lizzaalimeen
  37,64,Innahaa shajaratun takhruju feee aslil Jaheem
  37,65,Tal'uhaa ka annahoo ru'oosush Shayaateen
  37,66,Fa innahum la aakiloona minhaa famaali'oona minhal butoon
  37,67,Summa inna lahum 'alaihaa lashawbam min hameem
  37,68,Summa inna marji'ahum la ilal Jaheem
  37,69,Innahum alfaw aabaaa'ahum daaalleen
  37,70,Fahum 'alaa aasaarihim yuhra'oon
  37,71,Wa laqad dalla qablahum aksarul awwaleen
  37,72,Wa laqad arsalnaa feehim munzireen
  37,73,Fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul munzareen
  37,74,Illaa 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen�(section 2)
  37,75,Wa laqad naadaanaa Noohun falani'mal mujeeboon
  37,76,Wa jajainaahu wa ahlahoo minal karbil 'azeem
  37,77,Wa ja'alnaa zurriyyatahoo hummul baaqeen
  37,78,Wa taraknaa 'alaihi fil aakhireen
  37,79,Salaamun 'alaa Noohin fil 'aalameen
  37,80,Innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
  37,81,Innahoo min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
  37,82,Summa aghraqnal aakhareen
  37,83,Wa ina min shee'atihee la Ibraaheem
  37,84,Iz jaaa'a Rabbahoo bi qalbin saleem
  37,85,Iz qaala li abeehi wa qawmihee maazaa ta'budoon
  37,86,A'ifkan aalihatan doonal laahi tureedoon
  37,87,Famaa zannukum bi Rabbil'aalameen
  37,88,Fanazara nazratan finnujoom
  37,89,Faqaala inee saqeem
  37,90,Fatawallaw 'anhu mudbireen
  37,91,Faraagha ilaaa aalihatihim faqaala alaa taakuloon
  37,92,Maa lakum laa tantiqoon
  37,93,Faraagha 'alaihim darbam bilyameen
  37,94,Fa aqbalooo ilaihi yaziffoon
  37,95,Qaala ata'budoona maa tanhitoon
  37,96,Wallaahu khalaqakum wa maa ta'maloon
  37,97,Qaalub noo lahoo bun yaanan fa alqoohu fil jaheem
  37,98,Fa araadoo bihee kaidan faja 'alnaahumul asfaleen
  37,99,Wa qaala innee zaahibun ilaa Rabbee sa yahdeen
  37,100,Rabbi hab lee minas saaliheen
  37,101,Fabashsharnaahu bighulaamin haleem
  37,102,Falamma balagha ma'a hus sa'ya qaala yaa buniya inneee araa fil manaami anneee azbahuka fanzur maazaa taraa; qaala yaaa abatif 'al maa tu'maru satajidunee in shaaa'allaahu minas saabireen
  37,103,Falammaaa aslamaa wa tallahoo liljabeen
  37,104,Wa naadainaahu ai yaaaa Ibraheem
  37,105,Qad saddaqtar ru'yaa; innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
  37,106,Inna haazaa lahuwal balaaa'ul mubeen
  37,107,Wa fadainaahu bizibhin 'azeem
  37,108,Wa taraknaa 'alaihi fil aakhireen
  37,109,Salaamun 'alaaa Ibraaheem
  37,110,Kazaalika najzil muhsineen
  37,111,Innahoo min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
  37,112,Wa bashsharnaahu bi Ishaaqa Nabiyayam minas saaliheen
  37,113,Wa baaraknaa 'alaihi wa 'alaaa Ishaaq; wa min zurriyya tihimaa muhsinunw wa zaalimul linafshihee mubeen�(section 3)
  37,114,Wa laqad mananna alaa Moosaa wa Haaroon
  37,115,Wa najjainaahumaa wa qawmahumaa minal karbil 'azeem
  37,116,Wa nasarnaahum fakaanoo humul ghaalibeen
  37,117,Wa aatainaahumal Kitaabal mustabeen
  37,118,Wa hadainaahumus Siraatal Mustaqeem
  37,119,Wa taraknaa 'alaihimaa fil aakhireen
  37,120,Salaamun 'alaa Moosaa wa Haaroon
  37,121,Innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
  37,122,Innahumaa min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
  37,123,Wa inna Ilyaasa laminal mursaleen
  37,124,Iz qaala liqawmiheee alaa tattaqoon
  37,125,Atad'oona Ba'lanw wa tazaroona ahsanal khaaliqeen
  37,126,Allaaha Rabbakum wa Rabba aabaaa'ikumul awwaleen
  37,127,Fakazzaboohu fa inna hum lamuhdaroon
  37,128,Illaa 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
  37,129,Wa taraknaa 'alaihi fil aakhireen
  37,130,Salaamun 'alaaa Ilyaaseen
  37,131,Innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
  37,132,Innahoo min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
  37,133,Wa inna Lootal laminal mursaleen
  37,134,Iz najjainaahu wa ahlahooo ajma'een
  37,135,Illaa 'ajoozan fil ghaabireen
  37,136,Summa dammarnal aakhareen
  37,137,Wa innakum latamurroona 'alaihim musbiheen
  37,138,Wa billail; afalaa ta'qiloon�(section 4)
  37,139,Wa inna Yoonusa laminal mursaleen
  37,140,Iz abaqa ilal fulkil mash hoon
  37,141,Fasaahama fakaana minal mudhadeen
  37,142,Faltaqamahul hootu wa huwa muleem
  37,143,Falaw laaa annahoo kaana minal musabbiheen
  37,144,Lalabisa fee batniheee ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon
  37,145,Fanabaznaahu bil'araaa'i wa huwa saqeem
  37,146,Wa ambatnaa 'alaihi shajaratam mai yaqteen
  37,147,Wa arsalnaahu ilaa mi'ati alfin aw yazeedoon
  37,148,Fa aamanoo famatta' naahum ilaa heen
  37,149,Fastaftihim ali Rabbikal banaatu wa lahumul banoon
  37,150,Am khalaqnal malaaa'i kata inaasanw wa hm shaahidoon
  37,151,Alaaa innahum min ifkihim la yaqooloon
  37,152,Waladal laahu wa innhum lakaaziboon
  37,153,Astafal banaati 'alal baneen
  37,154,Maa lakum kaifa tahkumoon
  37,155,Afalaa tazakkaroon
  37,156,Am lakum sultaanum mubeen
  37,157,Faatoo bi Kitaabikum in kuntum saadiqeen
  37,158,Wa ja'aloo bainahoo wa bainal jinnati nasabaa; wa laqad 'alimatil jinnatu innahum lamuhdaroon
  37,159,Subhaanal laahi 'ammaa yasifoon
  37,160,Illaa 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
  37,161,Fa innakum wa maa ta'ubdoon
  37,162,Maaa antum 'alaihi befaaatineen
  37,163,Illaa man huwa saalil jaheem
  37,164,Wa maa minnasa illaa lahoo maqaamum ma'loom
  37,165,Wa innaa llanah nus saaffoon
  37,166,Wa innaa lanah nul musabbihoon
  37,167,Wa in kaanoo la yaqooloon
  37,168,Law anna 'indana zikram minal awwaleen
  37,169,Lakunna 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
  37,170,Fakafaroo bihee fasawfa ya'lamoon
  37,171,Wa laqad sabaqat Kalimatunaa li'ibaadinal mursa leen
  37,172,Innaa hum lahumul mansooroon
  37,173,Wa inna jundana lahumul ghaaliboon
  37,174,Fatawalla 'anhum hatta heen
  37,175,Wa absirhum fasawfa yubsiroon
  37,176,Afabi'azaabinaa yasta'jiloon
  37,177,Fa izaa nazala bisaahatihim fasaaa'a sabaahul munzareen
  37,178,Wa tawalla 'anhum hattaa heen
  37,179,Wa absir fasawfa yubsiroon
  37,180,Subhaana Rabbika Rabbil 'izzati 'amma yasifoon
  37,181,Wa salaamun 'alalmursaleen
  37,182,Walhamdu lillaahi Rabbil 'aalameen�(section 5)
